<p><strong>Details of the new charges from July 2017</strong></p>
<p>Up to 1 hour - 2.50</p>
<p>Up to 2 hours - 3.50</p>
<p>Up to 4 hours - 5.50</p>
<p>Up to 6 hours - 6.00</p>
<p>Up to 8 hours - 8.00</p>
<p>More than 8 hours - 10.00</p>
<p><strong>Parking for Blue Badge holders</strong> remains free until further notice, whilst additional pay &amp; display ticket machines are installed, after which the same charges will apply to all carpark users including Blue Badge holders.</p>
